{
  "stem": "9156.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My younger sister was in London.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father had died.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't think I said that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My father died already in the second year of the Nazi-- there's another story.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he died in a hospital from a heart attack because it was-- but I decided the best thing is to go to my mother.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were such horrible things, like the crystal night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know whether they smashed in our windows or not.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know, but it was all around.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Also, there was a neighbor whom my father had saved when the Nazis were not yet in power and tried to beat him up because he had said something bad, so my father had called the police and had helped him.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That neighbor wouldn't talk to him anymore and practically spit on him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My father was, with all his anger and all that, also very sensitive.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He had a heart condition, but that was too much.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And his children-- he had come and visited me in Hamburg.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, these are things I didn't tell all the detail.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he had met Paul, whom he did not want because he was not a Jew, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, in that respect, I felt Jews were just as prejudiced as anybody else.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he didn't want me to be with Paul.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But this was already Nazi time, and my-- just the first year.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Paul showed him around, and my father loved him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's a strange thing that I was told when he died, he was calling for both me and Paul.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So in spite of that, people can also learn to forget prejudices.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I didn't tell that because I can't tell everything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Back to my mother in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
